# 🇳🇵 Nepal Election Results 2082 Dashboard

A premium, real-time tracking dashboard for the **2082 BS (2026) House of Representatives** elections in Nepal. This project features a high-fidelity dark interface designed for data clarity and aesthetic appeal.

## ✨ Key Features
* **Live Parliament Chart:** Dynamic SVG donut chart showing the 138-seat majority threshold.
* **Constituency Search:** Advanced filtering by Province, Party, and Candidate name.
* **Hot Seats Tracking:** Dedicated monitoring of high-profile battles (e.g., Balen Shah vs. KP Oli).
* **Cross-Source AI Analysis:** A simulated real-time analysis feed verifying data across 12 sources.
* **News Feed:** Verified news ticker and source monitoring panel.
* **Responsive Design:** Fully optimized for Mobile, Tablet, and Desktop.

## 🛠️ Technical Stack
* **HTML5/CSS3:** Custom properties (variables) and complex animations.
* **Vanilla JavaScript:** Clean logic for data filtering, DOM manipulation, and clock synchronization.
* **Google Fonts:** Noto Serif Devanagari, JetBrains Mono, and Outfit.

## 🚀 Deployment
This site is designed to be hosted on **GitHub Pages**. Data is currently simulated for the 2082 election cycle context.

## ⚖️ Disclaimer
This is a data visualization project. All election data displayed is based on the provided 2082 BS scenario for development and demonstration purposes.